# Hichi üôè

A powerful CLI tool for interacting with Groq AI models through your terminal.

## Features

- üîê Secure password authentication
- üîë Encrypted API key storage
- üí¨ Interactive chat sessions with session-only memory
- ü§ñ Default model: openai/gpt-oss-120b
